


to extract snps from combined vcf file


vcftools --vcf combined.vcf --minQ 20 --minDP 10 --recode --recode-INFO-all --remove-indels --out snps_only


to extract indels from combined vcf file


vcftools --vcf combined.vcf --minQ 20 --minDP 10 --recode --recode-INFO-all --keep-only-indels --out indels.vcf

